balanceOf(address,uint256).details: See {IERC1155-balanceOf}. Requirements: - `account` cannot be the zero address.

balanceOfBatch(address[],uint256[]).details: See {IERC1155-balanceOfBatch}. Requirements: - `accounts` and `ids` must have the same length.

build(address,uint256,uint256,bool,uint2.details: This interacts with an Overlay Market to register oi and hold  positions on behalf of users.
build(address,uint256,uint256,bool,uint2.notice: Build a position on Overlay with OVL collateral

params._collateral: The amount of OVL to use as collateral in the position.
params._isLong: Whether to take out a position on the long or short side.
params._leverage: The amount of leverage to use in the position
params._market: The address of the desired market to interact with.
params._oiMinimum: Minimum acceptable amount of OI after impact and fees.

returns.positionId_: Id of the built position for on chain convenience.

exists(uint256).details: Indicates weither any token exist with a given id, or not.

liquidate(uint256,address).details: Interacts with an Overlay Market to exit all open interest associated with a liquidatable positoin.

params._positionId: ID of the position being liquidated.
params._rewardsTo: Address to send liquidation reward to.

totalSupply(uint256).details: Total amount of tokens in with a given id.

unwind(uint256,uint256).details: Interacts with a market contract to realize the PnL on a position.
unwind(uint256,uint256).notice: Unwinds shares of an existing position.

params._positionId: Id of the position to be unwound.
params._shares: Number of shars to unwind from the position.

uri(uint256).details: See {IERC1155MetadataURI-uri}. This implementation returns the same URI for *all* token types. It relies on the token type ID substitution mechanism https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-1155#metadata[defined in the EIP]. Clients calling this function must replace the `\{id\}` substring with the actual token type ID.

value(uint256).details: Gets price frame, total open interest and  total open interest shares from an Overlay market.
value(uint256).notice: Retrieves required information from market contract  to calculate position value with.

params._positionId: ID of position to determine value of.
